  "prompt": "How can I get rid of ant problems in my house?",
  "response": "Here are several ways to get rid of ants:\n\n1. Natural methods:\n- Vinegar and water solution\n- Cinnamon\n- Peppermint oil\n- Lemon juice\n- Diatomaceous earth\n- Chalk lines\n\n2. Chemical solutions:\n- Ant baits\n- Ant sprays\n- Borax and sugar mixtures\n- Insecticide powders\n\n3. Prevention techniques:\n- Seal entry points\n- Keep kitchen clean\n- Store food in airtight containers\n- Remove standing water\n- Trim plants near house\n- Clean up spills immediately\n\n4. Professional solutions:\n- Hire pest control service\n- Use professional-grade treatments\n\n5. Specific steps:\n- Identify ant type\n- Locate and block entry points\n- Remove food sources\n- Use targeted treatments\n- Maintain cleanliness\n\n6. Additional tips:\n- Keep counters and floors clean\n- Take out trash regularly\n- Fix water leaks\n- Use a dehumidifier\n- Regularly inspect potential entry areas\n\nCombining multiple methods usually provides the most effective ant control.",
